{
  "text": "Let F be an arbitrary field. In order to classify the 6-dimensional nilpotent Lie algebras over F, we determine the isomorphism classes of the 6-dimensional descendants of the nilpotent Lie algebras with dimension at most 5. In this section we summarize the result by listing these isomorphism classes for each of the Lie algebras with dimension at most 5, while in the Section 5 we provide with a detailed proof. The notation we use to describe nilpotent Lie algebras of dimension at most 5 is the same as in [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
